				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\mathcal {C}_{3}$\end{document}) are respected, the cost saving is reduced by about ten points, which corresponds to a loss of $1.6 in 1 year. At the same time, 30% (resp. 51%) of the battery initial SOH is preserved per year, equivalent to $13 (resp. $20) cost saving each year under C2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
